    Represents all the default recognized ServerOutputLines for the Minecraft Server.

    This enum class implements the ServerOutputLineType interface, and therefore follows all its conventions.

    These Defaults are interpreted last in the ServerOutputLine listener, meaning that each enumeration can be overwritten as necessary.
